## 🛑 STOP-WORDS → Hierarkisk Lookup

**När du ser error code, SÖK DIREKT i rätt fil:**

### HTTP Status Codes
- **406 Not Acceptable** → `@file .cursor/rules/core-rules.mdc` → §12 PostgREST Troubleshooting
- **401 Unauthorized** → `@file .cursor/rules/core-rules.mdc` → §0.5 Edge Functions JWT
- **403 Forbidden** → `@file .cursor/rules/core-rules.mdc` → §5 RLS Policies

### PostgREST Error Codes
- **PGRST106** → `@file .cursor/rules/core-rules.mdc` → §12 (Schema not exposed)
- **PGRST301** → `@file .cursor/rules/core-rules.mdc` → §5 (RLS violation)

### PostgreSQL Error Codes
- **42P01** (relation does not exist) → `@file .cursor/rules/core-rules.mdc` → §1 Schema Reality Check
- **42501** (insufficient privilege) → `@file .cursor/rules/core-rules.mdc` → §5 RLS
- **42883** (function does not exist) → `@file .cursor/rules/core-rules.mdc` → §1 Schema Reality Check

### Language Detection / Spam Filtering (OpenRouter LLM - Updated 2026-02-01)
- **Spam videos passing through** → `@file .cursor/rules/core-rules.mdc` → §0.65 Language Detection
- **OPEN_ROUTER_API** → `@file .cursor/rules/core-rules.mdc` → §0.65 Language Detection
- **Valid videos rejected** → `@file .cursor/rules/core-rules.mdc` → §0.65 Language Detection (Bypass Rules)

### YouTube Pipeline / fetch2 Integration (CRITICAL 2026-01-27)
- **⚠️ fetch2 NOT integrated** → `@file .cursor/rules/FETCH2_INTEGRATION_CRITICAL_2026-01-27.md`
- **0 videos from trusted channels** → fetch2 missing from Inngest workflow
- **Per-channel incremental** → fetch2 needs individual timestamps per channel
- **youtube_channel_config** → EXCEPTION LIST (not whitelist!)

### Supabase Security Advisor Codes
- 🛑 **0011 function_search_path_mutable** → Function lacks SET search_path → `@file .cursor/rules/core-rules.mdc` → §0 Absoluta krav + §5.5
- 🛑 **0010 security_definer_view** → View is SECURITY DEFINER → `@file .cursor/rules/core-rules.mdc` → §5.5 (often false positive for this project)

